\c 25
\s Mapoka avaimbi
\p
\v 1 Dhavhidhi navakuru vehondo vakatsaurirawo basa ravo vanakomana vaAsafi naHemani naJedhutuni, kuti vaporofite nembira, nemitengeramwa, namakandira; mazita avakabata basa ravo ndiwo:
\v 2 Vavanakomana vaAsafi: Zakuri, naJosefa, naNetania, naAsharera, vanakomana vaAsafi; vairairwa naAsafi, waiporofita nomurairo wamambo.
\v 3 VaJedhutuni: Vanakomana vaJedhutuni. Gedharia, naZeri, naJeshaya, naHashabhia, naMatitia, vatanhatu; ivo vairairwa nababa vavo Jedhutuni, nembira, waiporofita achivonga nokurumbidza Jehovha.
\v 4 VaHemani: Vanakomana vaHemani: Bhukia, naMatania, naUzieri, naShebhueri, naJerimoti, naHanania, naHanani, naEriata, naGidhareti, naRomamitiezeri, naJoshibhekasha, naMaroti, naHotiri, naMahazioti.
\v 5 Ava vese vakange vari vanakomana vaHemani muoni wamambo pamashoko aMwari; Mwari akapa Hemani vanakomana vane gumi navana, navakunda vatatu, kuzomusimbisa.
\v 6 Ava vese vairairwa nababa vavo pakuimba kwavo paimba yaJehovha namakandira, nemitengeramwa, nembira, pabasa reimba yaMwari; Asafi, naJedhutuni, naHemani vairairwa namambo.
\v 7 Ava vese, pamwe chete nehama dzavo dzakange dzadzidziswa kuimbira Jehovha, ivo vese vakange vachigona kwazvo, vakasvika mazana maviri namakumi masere navasere.
\p
\v 8 Vakakanda mijenya kuzoratidzwa mabasa avo, kusina anodarikwa, vadiki pamwe chete navakuru, navadzidzisi pamwe chete navadzidzi.
\v 9 Mujenya wokutanga waAsafi ukabata Josefa; wechipiri Gedharia; iye navanin'ina vake vakange vari gumi navaviri;
\v 10 wechitatu Zakuri, navanakomana vake navanin'ina vake, gumi navaviri;
\v 11 wechina Iziri, navanakomana vake navanin'ina vake, gumi navaviri;
\v 12 weshanu Netania, navanakomana vake navanin'ina vake, gumi navaviri;
\v 13 wetanhatu Bhukia, navanakomana vake, navanin'ina vake, gumi navaviri;
\v 14 wechinomwe Jesharera, navanakomana vake navanin'ina vake, gumi navaviri;
\v 15 worusere Jeshaya, navanakomana vake navanin'ina vake, gumi navaviri;
\v 16 wepfumbamwe Matania, navanakomana vake navanin'ina vake, gumi navaviri;
\v 17 wegumi Shimei, navanakomana vake navanin'ina vake, gumi navaviri;
\v 18 wegumi neumwe Azareri, navanakomana vake navanin'ina vake, gumi navaviri;
\v 19 wegumi navaviri Hashabhia, navanakomana vake navanin'ina vake, gumi navaviri;
\v 20 wegumi navatatu Shubhaeri, navanakomana vake navanin'ina vake, gumi navaviri;
\v 21 wegumi navana Matitia, navanakomana vake, navanin'ina vake, gumi navaviri;
\v 22 wegumi navashanu Jeremoti, navanakomana vake navanin'ina vake, gumi navaviri;
\v 23 wegumi navatanhatu Hanania, navanakomana vake navanin'ina vake, gumi navaviri;
\v 24 wegumi navanomwe Joshibhekasha, navanakomana vake navanin'ina vake, gumi navaviri;
\v 25 wegumi navasere Hanani, navanakomana vake navanin'ina vake, gumi navaviri;
\v 26 wegumi navapfumbamwe Maroti, navanakomana vake navanin'ina vake, gumi navaviri;
\v 27 wamakumi maviri Eriati, navanakomana vake navanin'ina vake, gumi navaviri;
\v 28 wamakumi maviri neumwe Hotiri, navanakomana vake navanin'ina vake, gumi navaviri;
\v 29 wamakumi maviri navaviri Gidhareti, navanakomana vake navanin'ina vake, gumi navaviri;
\v 30 wamakumi maviri navatatu Mahazioti, navanakomana vake navanin'ina vake, gumi navaviri;
\v 31 wamakumi maviri navana Romamitiezeri, navanakomana vake navanin'ina vake, gumi navaviri.
